:

1. *Vrata* su se otvarala polako. (The door opened slowly.)
2. Otvorio je *vrata*. (He opened the door.)
3. Ona je stajala ispred *vrata*. (She was standing in front of the door.)
4. Prošli smo kroz *vrata*. (We went through the door.)
5. Pokucao sam na *vrata*. (I knocked on the door.)
6. *Vrata* su zaključana. (The door was locked.)
7. Prilazila je *vratima*. (She was approaching the door.)
8. *Vrata* su se zatvorila. (The door closed.)